What’s the character delimiter? Answer: “,”

Is there a row for column names? Answer: There’s no row for column names.But in the description of the data, there’s information about each attributes.

Are there any missing values? If so, how are they codified? Answer: No. There is no missing values.

What is the data type of each column? Answer: They are nominal, continuous, continuous, continuous, continuous, continuous, continuous, continuous, integer.
